<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361560" n="1"/>
<salute>
   <lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustriss.</abbr> et <abbr>Celeber</abbr>. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Nicolao Bernoullj</rs>
   <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus <abbr>Antus.</abbr> Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
            </salute>
<p>
   <lb/>Non dubito quin meas acceperis <rs type="letters" key="B_1718-01-06_991170517037705501 B_1718-01-05_991170517037905501">literas</rs> Vir Ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cissime. Heri accepi a <abbr>Claris.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruele</rs> Tuo
   <lb/>hanc quam mitto <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs><note type="internal">Brief von NicII an Michelotti nicht erhalten, als nachgewiesenen Brief erfassen</note>. Ille me certio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem facit de <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_AEY8AYFA">dissertatione</rs> quam Celeber.
   <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> Tuus de Phosphoro parat, nunciatque
   <lb/>mihi <abbr>Illustr.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrem</rs> ejus mihi faviturum
               <lb/>in lectione scriptorum meorum: addit se
   <lb/>sperare de promotione ad <rs type="organisation">cathedram <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2934691">Duis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>burgensem</rs></rs>; quod mihi pergratum erit quando
               <lb/>uti spero, continget.
            </p>
<closer>Vale Vir <abbr>Celeberrime.</abbr> <dateline>Da<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bam <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice>
   <date when="1719-01-14">14 Januarii {1718-1719} <choice><abbr>m. v.</abbr><expan>more veneto</expan></choice></date></dateline><note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf</abbr>. den 15<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></foreign></note>
</closer>
<postscript>
<p>
<lb/>P. S.
   <lb/>Saluta Mem. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenum</rs> nomine meo, ipsique dic
   <lb/>(si huc venies) annon ipsi amplius opus sit <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_MJFBHDTR">Optic.</rs>
   <lb/>Cl. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-117444766">Wolfii</rs> quam ni fallor ante duos annos
                  <lb/>a me legendam petiit; adde me semper esse para<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissimum ad ejus mandata.
               </p>
</postscript>
